                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Bracus Horu\u0027usk was a Cabal who was Taken by Oryx during his assault on the Cabal of Mars and Phobos. Oryx would sever Horu\u0027usk from his leaders and elevate him to the Court of Oryx, where Horu\u0027usk\u0027s command would grant him power."
                  },
