                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Cra\u0027adug was originally a Hive Knight, dyad-bound to Mengoor. As members of the Court of Oryx, the two Knights would help tear down the Gift Mast, but they tithed its power to each other instead of Oryx. To teach them a lesson Oryx would Take Cra\u0027adug, and let Mengoor observe Cra\u0027adug\u0027s shape, to learn the path to the Final Shape of the universe."
                            },
