                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The two Hive Knights Mengoor and Cra\u0027adug fought side by side from their earliest days to their last. Oryx cursed them after they tithed their victories to each other instead of him, but they never gave up their camaraderie."
