                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Vorlog was a Hive Knight and member of the Court of Oryx. His accomplishments were so great that Oryx defined his name as meaning \u0022Less Than Me\u0022, so that Vorlog would never think of himself as greater than Oryx."
                  },
