                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Alzok was a Hive Wizard and sister to Gornuk and Zyrok. Together they were even older than the daughters of Oryx, and members of the Court of Oryx alongside them. She would lead her sisters on the path to make death their coven."
