                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Gornuk D\u00E4l was a Hive Wizard and sister to Alzok and Zyrok. As members of Oryx\u0027s Court, they were very powerful and sought to evade death. As the sisters cut their deaths away in a ritual, Gornuk consecrated their singing with black fire and gray blade."
