                              "value": "Material Space"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Zyrok was a Hive Wizard and sister to Alzok and Gornuk. They were members of the Court of Oryx, and after having cut their deaths away in order to cheat death, she would describe to Oryx how they had hidden their deaths in each other. That way, if any of them died, as long as one of them lived the others would live again too."
