                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Balw\u00FBr was a Hive Wizard and a daughter of Savath\u00FBn, the Witch Queen. Balw\u00FBr had become a servant of Oryx and was placed in his Court, where she would arm the members of the Court with weapons and poisons. "
