                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Ir Halak was a twin with her sister Ir An\u00FBk, and they were daughters of Oryx and members of his Court. Ir Halak would unravel the fabric of space and would leave worlds in tatters."
