                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Ir An\u00FBk was a Hive Wizard and twin sister to Ir Halak. As daughters of Oryx, they had become members of his Court. Ir An\u00FBk was attempting to learn to turn one of the eleven axioms of the Ascendant Plane false through her power."
