                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Ta\u0027aun was the Primus of the Skyburners legion. He was the mightiest Cabal in the solar system at the time of the Taken War, and after intentionally crashing into the Dreadnaught in order to infiltrate it he was Taken by Oryx. He was sent to test the worth of the Young Wolf, and attempt to kill them in Oryx\u0027s name, alongside Baxx."
                            },
