                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Baxx was originally an Unborn Ogre who failed in his task to protect the Chamber of Night. Oryx saw the potential in Baxx if he was freed from his fears, and would Take Baxx and assign him to act as one of Oryx\u0027s Hands. Baxx would fight alongside Ta\u0027aun against the Young Wolf two separate times, attempting to avenge Crota\u0027s death. "
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterVariant",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Material Space"
                            }
                          ]
                        }
                      ],
