                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny 2: Lightfall"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Sizmic, the Net-Desecrator"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Sizmic was a powerful Psion of the Shadow Legion who channeled his power into an array made of a Crux of Darkness in order to try to hack into the CloudArk. His attempts were foiled by both Vex and Guardians, and eventually he would be defeated by the Guardians when he tried to defend the array from their onslaught."
                  }
                ]
              }
