              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Hiraks was once a dreg of the House of Exile. After falling into the Hellmouth on Earth\u0027s moon, he became obsessed with the Hive and their magic. He studied their ways and would learn to use the Sword Logic to gain power. After becoming a Scorned Baron, he would begin to slay powerful beings in order to become Ascendant."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
