          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Kranox was an ancient and powerful Hive Knight. He held the key to the World\u0027s Grave, which was the Hive\u0027s archive containing all the knowledge of their vast conquests throughout history. He was a member of the Hidden Swarm, and would be stationed in the Hellmouth on Luna during their preparations to invade Earth."
        },
