                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Dakoor was the Hive Knight representing the Worm God Yul, the Honest Worm. Together with the other Swarm Princes he led the Hidden Swarm, and helped to create the sword of Crota himself."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
