                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Garok was the Hive Knight representing the Worm God Xol, Will of the Thousands. He wielded a Cleaver as he fought alongside his fellow Princes and led the Hidden Swarm in servitude of their master Sardon, and by extension Crota."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
