                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Merok was the Hive Knight representing the Worm God Eir, the Keeper of Order. He and the other Swarm Princes were assigned to protect the sword of Crota in his absence, but would meet their end whilst doing so as a Guardian of the Last City hunted them down on their quest to destroy the sword."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
