        },
        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Disciples of Crota"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterVariant",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Material Space"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The God-Prince of the Hive Crota had a group of powerful disciples that followed him and were lead by his Will, Omnigul. They acted as commanders during the Spawn of Crota\u0027s invasion of Earth. "
        },
        {
          "alias": "groupMembers",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "6a296b4a-7935-4fc6-9c37-abbe0e78ab92",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Eyes of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Eyes of Crota were three powerful Acolytes, who had chosen to not morph into Knights or Wizards in order to remain small and hard to detect. They acted as spies for Crota, stealthily gathering information for their master\u0027s plans. "
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "groupMembers",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": {
                      "contentData": [
                        {
                          "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                          "key": "d5b273a5-227c-4149-b6a5-d9fdcc0fa52e",
                          "udi": null,
                          "values": [
                            {
                              "alias": "profilePicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": [
                                {
                                  "key": "45311774-c07f-4738-b06a-ec1fb0b2d3a7",
                                  "mediaKey": "b3ce379d-8cbf-4a63-9e44-cd7d750516e2",
                                  "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                                  "crops": [],
                                  "focalPoint": null
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterName",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Eye of Crota"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterVariant",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Material Space"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterSource",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Together with the other two Eyes of Crota, this powerful Acolyte would engage a Guardian of the Last City when they sought to gain loot in the Cosmodrome. What the Eyes hadn\u0027t realized was that this Guardian was actually there not for loot, but for them. They died to this Guardian, as a fitting punishment for spies who didn\u0027t have accurate enough information on their enemy\u0027s intentions."
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "mainPicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": [
                                {
                                  "key": "eea740f4-6231-43b5-b2f0-4098953cecad",
                                  "mediaKey": "430e48c1-0f9b-4fef-a75c-afd5261a02a2",
                                  "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                                  "crops": [],
                                  "focalPoint": null
                                }
                              ]
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                          "key": "2cfde270-0bfe-4d8e-a677-d405ba8238f5",
                          "udi": null,
                          "values": [
                            {
                              "alias": "profilePicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": [
                                {
                                  "key": "c68d0e51-30e4-4bb9-8a21-734ec39377ff",
                                  "mediaKey": "1ba95144-9df8-42e5-958d-c325c0a22e7f",
                                  "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                                  "crops": [],
                                  "focalPoint": null
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterName",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Eye of Crota"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterVariant",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Material Space"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterSource",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "This Acolyte was sent to gather intel within the Cosmodrome alongside his fellow Eyes. They were masters of stealth, but in the event of being attacked, they wielded powerful Boomers so they could leave no witnesses before escaping."
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "mainPicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": [
                                {
