                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Hand of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "3603ad25-f70c-40a5-aa36-0239f904accd",
                        "mediaKey": "3893243e-dd93-475d-9fe3-365c2b50e09e",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The right-hand Knight of Crota was powerful, but also clever. He would employ unorthodox strategies against the enemies of his master, ambushing them in the dark, and sending his horde of cursed Thrall at them. Once they were weakened from the accursed blasts and claw marks, the Hand would strike with his Cleaver to finish them off."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "46f417ec-4b49-4409-9fa6-e5e3ca000536",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Heart of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "ff15508a-44d3-4cb8-9dd7-20b79b1f9d02",
                        "mediaKey": "e3f7c6c8-518c-4cd7-8fbb-bcb497eb678b",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "aa8c4b26-79a0-45f8-a7b7-cae22155c1af",
                        "mediaKey": "559c7ad0-6114-4be7-8f9d-a189a02f489b",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Heart of Crota was a vile Wizard whose blood fed the fury of the Spawn of Crota. She personally stripped Omar Agah of his Light, feeding it to the newly spawned. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "a60996cf-0777-4f88-87d8-cc2c8dabed4c",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "4f0f9e5f-9f08-47eb-bca8-71b6b19ecb83",
                        "mediaKey": "d2a585e0-3507-4935-8d85-4e98c18953b8",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "05af3026-d3ef-4d7f-aae2-c6276dd84964",
                        "mediaKey": "c849ace0-b85a-4736-8591-54eebbc53aaf",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Might of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Summoned to leave only destruction in its path, the Might of Crota was wild and full of rage. He was created by Crota for the sole purpose of being untamable, even to the mighty Kagoor, Oryx\u0027s personal Ogre-tamer. During Omnigul\u0027s assault on the Warmind bunker under the Cosmodrome, a Guardian of the Last City interfered. Instead of capturing the Warmind as originally intended, Omnigul decided to let both the Warmind and the Guardian feel the utter devastation of Crota\u0027s Mighty Ogre. The Might was summoned, but would be defeated by the Guardian as Omnigul watched."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "6c3fcb4e-2d9f-4ad5-9044-9abffad19a6a",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "91ae8d75-8403-4869-8d3a-65860d9196e7",
                        "mediaKey": "354663cc-debc-4806-bfef-3d1189b783e6",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "60596ed8-419c-4fc6-8583-23009801c6b0",
                        "mediaKey": "1f181a14-f115-46f3-bf33-34259959f8da",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Sardon, Fist of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Sardon was the leader of the Blades of Crota, an army of powerful Knights. He also commanded his generals, the Swarm Princes. As the Fist of Crota, it was Sardon\u0027s duty to lead the fight of Crota\u0027s armies from the frontline. He and his Blades scarred the Moon with their power, and would go on to lead the Spawn of Crota\u0027s invasion of Earth."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "342c5ce2-9dff-4114-ae61-332ec6a22130",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Ir Y\u00FBt, the Deathsinger"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "As Crota\u0027s most cherished disciple, Ir Y\u00FBt mastered the Deathsong. She would perform her dark liturgy in the presence of any enemies of Crota, and their ruin would be invoked. She would spend time in the Oversoul Throne alongside Crota in the time leading up to the invasion of Earth, working with her master to plan for the conquest. "
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "8a8ec059-934a-4323-b5de-d1769f652c61",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "energyMultiplicator",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": ""
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "energyExponent",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": ""
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Omnigul, Will of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Mother of the Spawn, Herald of Crota"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "fb082f17-732f-416a-929e-8080937c44bf",
                        "mediaKey": "78984778-133e-49a9-ac69-7420d708f83f",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "01dbbf50-b07b-4739-9f2d-39c4919ff139",
                        "mediaKey": "d5563d06-51a0-4f0a-aeb4-6b306b6a1e89",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Omnigul was Crota\u0027s mate and the general of his armies. She led the Spawn of Crota. When Crota returned to the Oversoul Throne to prepare for the invasion of Earth, Omnigul remained in material space to oversee the seeding of Earth. Once the invasion began, she fought on the frontlines, and directly led a capture team into the Warmind bunker under the Cosmodrome. After being forced to retreat at the hands of a Guardian, she would use the knowledge she gained to prepare for their inevitable attack on her lair. When the Guardian arrived, she would avoid direct confrontation for extended periods of time. Instead she would perform quick strikes, and between strikes teleport away and send swarms of servants to surprise her enemy. "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
