            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Haroktha was originally a Krill on Fundament who accepted a worm larva from Xivu Arath and grew to become one of the first Hive Knights. He fought against the rival Krill kingdom of the Helium Drinkers, and would go on to serve Xivu Arath for billions of years. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
