        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Disciples of the Witness"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Saviours serving existance"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Witness had a group of followers who all served its ultimate goal of the Final Shape in various ways. These beings were collectively some of the most powerful beings in the universe after the Witness itself."
        },
        {
          "alias": "groupMembers",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "7129a2c5-3425-4e5e-9bab-d9f39817c9ba",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Rhulk, Disciple of the Witness"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Subjugator"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny 2: The Witch Queen"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "1b8864c3-1ada-415a-8cd2-155ad422e390",
                        "mediaKey": "a2eb3070-79fe-4cf4-a4e2-cbce37b4830b",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "772d3da0-1768-40ee-8d6e-21301d0660d5",
                        "mediaKey": "1d4b2fee-c2fe-4e04-8f34-edf7e48355af",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Rhulk was the first being the Witness gave the title of disciple to. He proved his worth and loyalty to the Witness by destroying his home world of Lubrae and becoming the last of his species left in the universe. He subjugated the Worm Gods, and took Xita to his Pyramid Ship. There he would harvest worm larvae for the armies of the Hive, as he was ordered to by the Witness."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "1bc6a9d8-d508-4a2f-a1eb-bdd331806688",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "b15f3939-58d7-47a4-b2b7-01424bbce55b",
                        "mediaKey": "bf1a0a52-c9be-463b-97a8-372970069b57",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Calus, the Disciple"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Exiled Emperor, Herald of the Witness"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny 2: Lightfall"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "f2d0201f-7e98-4a0b-b763-37598d1f116c",
                        "mediaKey": "a81d813f-f0d3-4bdf-9550-46e731f6dbe4",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Calus was previously the Emperor of the Cabal Empire, and ruled it for centuries before the Midnight Coup exiled him. In his exile he encountered the Witness, who promised him that he would one day be the last living being watching as the universe came to its Final Shape. After years of working to help the Witness with its goals, he would be crowned a disciple by the Witness, granting him access to the incredible powers of the Darkness."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "c4efce17-afd8-4873-a2dc-fa5a6487847c",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
