        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Vex\u0027s main ground unit is the Goblin. Their metallic hulls can withstand serious damage, but they are not made for combat. Goblins work with their Axis Minds to help transform celestial bodies into Machine-Worlds that bind the Vex Network to Material Space."
        },
