          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Hobgoblins have improved optics and acute sensors in their horns, making their targeting better for long-range. They use this to help their Axis Minds build structures over longer distances, or to snipe enemies who interfere."
        }
      ]
    },
