                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny 2: The Edge of Fate"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Giver\u0027s Bounty"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Exile Prime Servitor"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Giver\u0027s Bounty was the Prime Servitor of the House of Exile on Luna. It was taken by Levaszk to Kepler when he sought to give new hope to the House. The Prime would be named after the \u0022Giver\u0022, which was Levaszk\u0027s name for Earth\u0027s member of the Nine \u0022III\u0022. Levaszk believed his House was being blessed by the Giver, and the Prime Servitor was imbued with its power to manipulate dark matter. "
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
