          "segment": null,
          "value": "Servitor"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Servitors are made by the Fallen in the image of the Traveler. They use energy and matter to create Ether, a resource the Fallen need for life. Due to their importance, Servitors are built with strong armor plating."
        },
