          "segment": null,
          "value": "Psion"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Psions were enslaved by the Cabal Empire long ago, and became important members of their military. They have psionic powers, able to wield telekinesis and speak telepathically. They often act as engineers and mechanics due to their smaller size and hyper-intellect."
        }
      ]
    },
