          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Incendiors wear magma launchers, and carry heavy fuel packs on their backs. They can use their launcher to literally launch people away on top of launching chunks of hot magma at them. They wear armor similar to that of a typical Legionary."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
