          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "90a05745-395a-4358-9d97-0ad53f6745a0",
              "mediaKey": "85ce3f26-c4de-4315-89e1-cec75fda21ca",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Lieutenants of Ta\u0027aurc"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Siege Dancers legion was led by Valus Ta\u0027aurc, and serving beneath him were his four most powerful lieutenants, each with the rank of Val. "
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": ""
        },
        {
          "alias": "groupMembers",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "d8ff2610-15d7-481d-be7f-8ffc68140e22",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Val Bou\u0027urc"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "d51dc279-c33c-4d79-af67-25149fa8c463",
                        "mediaKey": "5c354773-a902-4bf7-a086-034302d086df",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Val Bou\u0027urc was stationed just outside of Firebase Rubicon when a Guardian fireteam attacked. The Guardians\u0027 main target was Valus Ta\u0027aurc, but before reaching him they took out Bou\u0027urc."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "59212630-5e22-4cd2-ae17-7008d27a14fb",
                        "mediaKey": "6d0ad398-3430-45ec-9f61-47c3b713ecd6",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "464d23ec-5535-4449-8fe2-fdb5672e8dae",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "4a1133dc-8c2f-44ba-afab-8ac64c643632",
                        "mediaKey": "859fb6ba-3dad-414a-ad86-d0a8cfcc59a5",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Val Zu\u0027uarc"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "20907633-9aaa-4883-b1fb-704e959b52a5",
                        "mediaKey": "68f32cb7-b3af-4fb8-bc89-5ff5a99fb26a",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Val Zu\u0027uarc was sent to the Trenchworks via a Harvester ship after his comrade Val Bou\u0027urc was slain by a Guardian fireteam there. He engaged the Guardians, and was reinforced by Val Ma\u0027aurg, and with their impenetrable shields the Guardians had to give it their all. Zu\u0027uarc died in the fight, failing to avenge Bou\u0027urc, and failing to protect his Valus from the attackers."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "d65ecbd3-ae17-4259-94cf-01b2fbccc923",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "ff52b0be-2fdd-48e4-b98b-ae893a2cd2bf",
                        "mediaKey": "73b24f07-6a9b-46ea-ba3c-0554ca2126e6",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "e0f5f0a3-406c-4a91-bf6d-c31f1b064a0f",
                        "mediaKey": "f67ca0bd-b060-475f-b5cc-a91a88d488c4",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Val Ma\u0027aurg"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Val Ma\u0027aurg was sent to reinforce Val Zu\u0027uarc as he battled against a Guardian fireteam. As a lieutenant of Valus Ta\u0027aurc, Ma\u0027aurg was fierce and wore strong armor. After Zu\u0027uarc fell however, Ma\u0027aurg\u0027s skills and strength ended up falling short. He was killed, failing to keep the fireteam from advancing towards Valus Ta\u0027aurc\u0027s Land Tank. Hope remained that the fourth lieutenant could stop the Guardians as he arrived in a Goliath Tank."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
