          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Gladiator"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Many Cabal fight in traditional fighting pits, gladitorial combat to both put on a show for an audience and to display their strength. Some bring the tactics of the pits into the war fronts, wielding sharp cleavers able to cut through even hard metals. Since they engage targets at point-blank range they have armor strong enough to survive reaching the enemy and cutting them down."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
