          "segment": null,
          "value": "After 200 years, a Hive will have reached the power needed to morph into a Knight. The natural exoskeleton of a Knight is incredibly dense, and they can channel their dark power into weapons like Boomers, firing bolts of rotten starfire at their enemies."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
