                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Imminent Mind"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Imminent Mind was made by the Vex of the distant future, the Descendants. It was a part of the Sol Progeny, and was made to harness a part of the Black Heart\u0027s power. It would have granted the Vex the ability to alter the future of the universe\u0027s timeline entirely."
                  }
                ]
              }
