                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Baxx, the Gravekeeper"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: The Taken King"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Baxx was an Ogre placed in the deepest part of the Chamber of Night after the fall of Crota. His purpose was to defend the site of the failed Wakening Ritual, and if he had succeeded he would have been Summoned into an Ascendant Ogre. During a fight against the Guardian who slew Crota, Oryx Took Baxx, having realized that the Ogre was doomed to fail otherwise. Baxx would experience a Summoning Ritual by the hand of Oryx directly."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
