              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Blighted Descendant"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny: The Taken King"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "In a vision of a distant future, the Guardian who slew Morphon would see what the Warlock Praedyth called \u0022the end of the Vex\u0022. In this future point in time, where the Guardian had failed to stop Oryx\u0027s Taken from infesting the Vault, they encountered a mysterious Taken Minotaur. This Minotaur was in control of the Vault of Glass, and had allowed Oryx access to all other timelines. This had lead to Oryx Taking all Vex throughout all versions of the Vex Network. The Blighted Descendant would be destroyed by the Guardian, who would never forget what they stopped in the Vault that day."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
