                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Valus Cal\u0027Dhur was a member of the Shadow Legion who managed to survive the initial battles against Neomuna. He was stationed inside the Typhon Imperator, using its Pyramid-technology to enhance his weapons and armor. He engaged a Guardian who entered the ship in order to disrupt the Shadow Legion\u0027s activities. During his fight, the powerful Valus showed his strategic prowess, using portable Cabal shields, switching weapons mid-fight and using the environment to his advantage."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
