          "segment": null,
          "value": "28"
        },
        {
          "alias": "profilePicture",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "579a1161-59ff-4e37-8ed6-78b4a05a1a0f",
              "mediaKey": "46a63d73-7237-4907-beeb-8de2e75ef795",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Ascendant Devil Splicers"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny: Rise of Iron"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Devil Splicers discovered SIVA, a nanotechnology from humanity\u0027s Golden Age. They began using it to enhance their weapons and armor, and would seek to perfect themselves in order to ascend to godhood. According to Vosik, the Archpriest of the Splicers, worlds would fall if more Splicers were perfected, showing the true potential of SIVA."
        },
        {
          "alias": "groupMembers",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "ad0da05a-e54e-47a6-9e8a-38826d40b830",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "e4383caf-06a5-4cb4-97b7-e1c0ba96c779",
                        "mediaKey": "156934ed-6004-44ad-8f08-fcabb90e91ea",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "40c5d6cd-c721-4855-99ac-53317410580b",
                        "mediaKey": "0c395276-6a0c-4ba1-81ae-47849aeac79e",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Kovik, Splicer Priest"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: Rise of Iron"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Kovik was the one who managed to figure out how to use SIVA to enhance himself and the other Splicers. Where Aksis would use this to make himself stronger, Kovik instead used this to experiment with the Hive. He managed to capture the Ogre leading the Silent Brood, and removed its eye from its head. He attached this eye to his Null Cannon, empowering it with the Ascendant strength of a Summoned Ogre. "
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "High Priest"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "5fbf3a51-25a9-4d9b-8f06-8d55b3d32af7",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "2e96c6bb-af40-49f7-95e3-59d47c7141f0",
                        "mediaKey": "3d4b0b4f-e087-43e2-98be-d4d3439de756",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "e2a28f79-2737-458f-b608-2e52e9849e3f",
                        "mediaKey": "7efb3215-bdee-4663-8321-c02d8aa462b3",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Aksis, Archon Prime"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny: Rise of Iron"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Aksis was the leader of the Devil Splicers. He used SIVA to ascend to a level of power beyond that of any other Fallen. Vosik would ensure that offerings of SIVA would be used to build and maintain Aksis\u0027s body, which had been altered so heavily by SIVA that there was no organic Eliksni matter left in it. Aksis was so extremely changed with SIVA that it started to take over his mind, controlling both the mind and his body. He was the first Eliksni to become 100% machine, which was considered divine to the Fallen who worshipped machines, but he lost himself to his own hunger for power. "
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Machine-God"
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "settingsData": [
