                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "The Infantine"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterVariant",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Material Space"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "characterSource",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Destiny: The Taken King"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "After suffering countless defeats at the hands of Guardians, a coven of Acolytes within the Blood of Oryx attempted to ascend a new champion. They began a Summoning Ritual that involved imbuing an infantine Ogre with Taken power. The Ritual succeeded right as a Guardian arrived trying to stop it, and they were forced to engage the Infantine in a battle. The mighty Ogre was able to cause tremors by slamming the ground, disorienting its opponent during the fight."
                            }
                          ]
                        }
