                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Sardok, Eye of Oryx"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterVariant",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Material Space"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Sardok was a powerful Knight assigned to protect the Lunar Shrine of Oryx. These shrines were how the Hive sent their tributes across the universe to Oryx\u0027s Dreadnaught, and were thus extremely important for his survival. To ensure its safety, one of the strongest Hive on the moon of Earth was required."
                  }
                ]
              },
