                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Three Ascendant Taken were assigned to serve D\u00FBl Incaru by working under Val Belyx. They defended a monastery in the Dreaming City where an easy access point to the Ascendant Plane could be found, protecting it from intruders. "
                  },
