                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Om Alir summoned hordes of Shadow Thrall to support her and the other Sentinels\u0027 defensive line within the Dreaming City. She personally acted as the last line of defense before an intruder could reach the inner parts of the monastery, and used a massive Blight to block the way."
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
