                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Aarta and the other Planeshifting Taken were defeated one by one by the same Guardian over the span of a week. The Guardian channeled their power into an Agonarch Rune that could summon them back again to try to defend their master Dumuzod."
