          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Panoptes, Infinite Mind"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2: Curse of Osiris"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Panoptes was the Vex Axis Mind in charge of the Infinite Forest. This was the vast simulation engine used by the Vex to figure out how to attain a future where they succeed at converting the entire universe to Vex machinery. This simulation engine consisted of an infinite amount of simulations, each being an entire timeline simulated to 100% accuracy, down to the smallest atom."
        },
        {
          "alias": "mainPicture",
          "culture": null,
