                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Gulrot, Unclean"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Gulrot was an Ogre Summoned by the Worm Keepers in the Prison of Elders. After being defeated by a fireteam of Guardians, Gulrot would be returned to its Throne World, and would be resummoned to material space by its servants in order to once again attempt to defeat the Lightbearers."
                            }
