                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Phogoth would never be seen again after his defeat in material space, but since he had just been Summoned his soul would have returned to his Throne World within the Ascendant Plane."
                            }
                          ]
                        },
                        {
                          "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
