                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "After killing Osiris\u0027s Ghost Sagira, The Hight Celebrant would be hunted by Guardians. It would enter the Ascendant Plane from the Dreaming City, and would use hordes of Hive to hold his enemies back.  "
                  },
                  {
