                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Ascendant Plane"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "After being defeated in material space and having his soul returned to his Throne World, its possible that Oryx Took Sardok and sent him back into material space as a Taken Knight named Krathoor, however his ultimate fate is unknown."
                  }
                ]
              },
