                    "value": "Destiny: House of Wolves"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "After being killed in material space, Urrox would suffer a final death in an unknown way by being killed inside his Throne World. This is evident as a Ghost would revive him in the Light and bring him back within the Prison of Elders years after his initial defeat there."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterTitle",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Scion of Oryx"
