                              "value": "After being slain in material space by the Young Wolf, Garok and two of the other Swarm Princes bound themselves in servitude to Savath\u00FBn. Within the Ascendant Plane they began conducting a ritual on an Ascendant Cleaver, but would be interrupted by the Young Wolf."
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "mainPicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": [
                                {
                                  "key": "9102860e-c955-4362-9f0b-2cfaf25a1b4d",
                                  "mediaKey": "6ab58629-25db-4902-a6da-0cce680b6771",
                                  "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                                  "crops": [],
                                  "focalPoint": null
                                }
                              ]
