                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Merok was one of the Swarm Princes who joined Savath\u00FBn after their defeat and the subsequent deaths of Crota and Oryx. During a ritual within the Ascendant Plane they were forced to engage the Young Wolf. Merok fought side-by-side with Dakoor against their killer, but they would meet their final deaths at the hands of the Traveler\u0027s chosen Guardian."
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "mainPicture",
                              "culture": null,
