                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The God-Prince of the Hive Crota had a group of powerful disciples that followed him and his Will, Omnigul. They acted as commanders during the Spawn of Crota\u0027s invasion of Earth. "
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "groupMembers",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": {
                      "contentData": [
                        {
                          "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
