                              "value": "Destiny: The Dark Below"
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Omnigul was summoned back into material space after her inital defeat at the hands of the Young Wolf. Her soul had survived in her Throne World within the Ascendant Plane, and she would attempt to retake control over the Cosmodrome upon returning."
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "profilePicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
