                              "value": ""
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Om Alir was, just like all others who assaulted the Dreaming City, stuck within the city\u0027s time loop. She would be returned to material space every three weeks to keep attempting to protect the monastery, but would keep failing and be sent back to the Ascendant Plane between attempts."
                            }
                          ]
                        },
