                    "value": "Destiny 2: Episode: Revenant"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "After being defeated in material space within the Prison of Elders, Sylok would linger in the Ascendant Plane and await his eventual return. During this time his appearance altered for unknown reasons. After his second defeat he would once again be returned to the Ascendant Plane, doomed to roam it without a clear purpose."
                  }
