                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "After being slain in material space by a Guardian, Crorok\u0027s soul was sent to the Ascendant Plane where all Taken souls truly reside in the Darkness. Crorok would be restored every three weeks however due to the time loop placed on the Dreaming City."
