                    "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Bracus Payne would be returned to the Ascendant Plane over and over again every time he was defeated in his attempts to invade the Dreaming City. Due to him being Taken, and never being faced in the Ascendant Plane by his enemies, he would never be permanently stopped."
                  },
