                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "A fireteam of Guardians used the Rift Generator to breach into the part of the Ascendant Plane where Vakarsik was being restored. They interrupted the ritual and Vakarsik engaged them in battle. After being defeated in the Ascendant Plane Vakarsik would have been gone forever, but due to the time loop the Dreaming City was plunged into he would be returned to his semi-restored state every three weeks to keep attempting to return again."
                  }
                ]
              },
