                              "alias": "details",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Sarkoor was found defending the Dreadnaught until the Young Wolf stole a shard of Crystal from the Chamber of Night. She was assigned by Oryx to channel her Ascendant power into six Tomb Husks which the Hive used to seal the doors that the Guardian attempted to flee through. She remained as a last line of defense at the exit to the Lunar fortress, assaulting the Young Wolf with her army of Shadow Thrall."
                            }
                          ]
