                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Drachna leads a group of Darkblades within the Ascendant Plane, working for D\u00FBl Incaru with an unclear task. Due to Quria\u0027s time loop Drachna and his servants return every three weeks to continue their dark purpose, even after being killed."
