                    "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The three Fatesmiths of D\u00FBl Incaru served her within Eleusinia. After their initial defeat, Quria\u0027s time loop brought them back, and they keep returning every three weeks to assist their master. Their fates are bound to D\u00FBl Incaru, allowing her to bring them back even mid-fight after they\u0027ve been killed."
                  },
