                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": "Gaurog was stationed atop a large watchtower alongside D\u00FBl Incaru and the other Fatesmiths. After their initial defeat at the hands of the Young Wolf, Quria\u0027s time loop brought them back. Every three weeks Gaurog returns to protect D\u00FBl Incaru again."
                            },
                            {
                              "alias": "mainPicture",
                              "culture": null,
                              "editorAlias": null,
                              "segment": null,
                              "value": [
                                {
                                  "key": "b479e81c-cc41-44d7-865e-d0bcfb3e32f5",
                                  "mediaKey": "2aff0294-f653-4c94-9b7f-d7fec40c1b21",
                                  "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                                  "crops": [],
                                  "focalPoint": null
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
