        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Court of Oryx\u0027s members were Ascendant, and thus had Throne Worlds of their own and wielded 5-Dimensional power in the Ascendant Plane accordingly."
