                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Bracus Horu\u0027usk"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "After being defeated by Guardians in material space, Bracus Horu\u0027usk was brought back to the Ascendant Plane. Guardians would keep summoning him into material space in order to obtain power artifacts in his possession, and his ultimate fate is unknown. "
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
