                    "value": "Ascendant Plane"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Lokaar would be returned to her Throne World and resummoned into material space countless times by greedy Guardians seeking to gain strength from the ancient secrets of the Hive. Whether she was ever killed in her Throne World or not is unknown."
