                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Whether or not Vorlog experienced a final death within the Ascendant Plane is unclear, as years after the Taken War he was brought back to life through Nokris\u0027s necromancy, a power that usually only brings back those who truly died. Vorlog has however never been seen actually dying within the Ascendant Plane."
