                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Thalnon would be summoned to the Dreadnaught by Guardians, who slew him using the same method as how they slew Crota. Unlike Crota however, it is unclear if Thalnok had a final death or not as he was never observed being killed in the Ascendant Plane."
