                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Ascendant Plane"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Years after being defeated aboard the Dreadnaught, Alak-Hul would be revived by a Ghost. Whether this suggests that he had also been killed within the Ascendant Plane or not is unknown. His ultimate fate is yet to be determined, as after being defeated in his Lightbearer form, his clever Ghost escaped, meaning that he might be revived again in the future."
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
