                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Golgoroth was stationed in the cellars of Oryx\u0027s Throne World. There he would watch over the Light captured by Oryx\u0027s forces, preparing it to be fed upon. Golgoroth would meet his end here however as a fireteam of Guardians reclaimed the Light and used it against the mighty Ogre."
                  },
