                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Within Oryx\u0027s Throne World the Warpriest acted as a test to any who desired to challenge Oryx where he was the strongest. Overcoming the Annihilator Totems and defeating the Warpriest was the only way to prove ones self worthy of facing the Taken King."
