          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Phylaks, the Warrior"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2: Beyond Light"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Phylaks was the commander of Eramis\u0027s military. She lived with an ideology that involved only fighting. She always sought to prove her skill in combat against the most dangerous foes, and when she gained access to a couple of Pyramid Splinters she would become even more adept at fighting. She would use Stasis to freeze her enemies in place, and then deliver a crushing blow using her personal Wire Rifle."
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Warrior of Darkness"
        }
      ]
    },
