          "segment": null,
          "value": "Little Nightmares 3"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Kin is a man who runs the Carnevale, a massive airship with a carnival on top. He wears a mask acquired from the Doctor, and makes sure that the Herd has entertainment to consume for an unclear reason. On his right arm he is missing a hand, instead having the Mini-Kin attached to it, whom the Kin takes care of through feeding him dead carnival goers. He has average strength for a resident of the Nowhere, but with his teamwork with the Mini-Kin he is adept at catching the visiting children and forcing them to entertain the Herd."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
      "key": "11db19d4-1449-42a5-965e-e4b41b611f66",
