          "segment": null,
          "value": "8"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sonic grew stronger over the years as he fought against Eggman\u0027s armies and various other threats. By the time of the Time Eater\u0027s attack, Sonic had become strong enough to single-handedly bring down robots like the Egg Emperor with only eight strikes."
        },
        {
