          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sonic Heroes"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The Egg Emperor was a robot built by Doctor Eggman with the purpose of allowing him to personally defend his flagship from attacks. It was used by Metal Sonic to battle against Sonic and his friends in order to copy the last bits of data that he hadn\u0027t finished copying previously. It was twice as strong as the original Egg Hawk, requiring two hundred strikes from Sonic to destroy at the time."
        }
      ]
    },
