        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Soldiers were built by the Ancients on the Starfall Islands to act as infantry that could defend their civilization from outside threats. The ones stationed on Kronos Island were the weakest in terms of durability, but they could still be a threat to most invaders."
        },
