        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "The TOWER guardian was stationed on Kronos Island and acted as a hinderance for any invading forces trying to assault the island on the ground. It was normally attached to the ground, but could lift itself out of the ground in order to hover and evade attacks. This could surprise and overwhelm attackers as the TOWER fired various weapons at its targets."
        }
      ]
    },
