          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sonic Frontiers"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Swimming around the sands of Ares Island were these shark-inspired guardians. They were heavily armored and fast, able to swiftly catch unsuspecting invaders as they suddenly burst out of the ground beneath them and used their massive jaws to bite apart the enemy."
        }
      ]
    },
