          "value": "EXCAVATOR"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sonic Frontiers"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "EXCAVATORs were variants of the TOWER guardian. They were stationed on Chaos Island and were equipped with advanced energy-based weapons that they would launch at any intruders who strayed too close to them. Only their heads were integral for their ability to function, with most of the body being nothing but a distraction for enemy fire."
        }
      ]
    },
