        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "SILVER HAMMERs were variants of the TOWER that would defend Ouranos Island from invaders. They had extensive weapons systems that they would use to overwhelm opponents as strikes of energy landed from above."
