        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "SUPREME"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Sonic Frontiers"
        },
        {
          "alias": "mainPicture",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "24785817-b852-4059-be5b-6389d37a9f2d",
              "mediaKey": "bc383ed0-774b-4fc7-84d3-b982f50b862d",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "SUPREME was the mightiest of the Titans built by the Ancients and was enhanced by the Chaos Emeralds\u0027 power. It sported a vast array of extremely advanced weapons, including a massive rifle it could fire beams of energy with. Its pilot would sacrifice himself and the Titan in order to absorb THE END into the titanic machine\u0027s body, allowing the other Titans to seal SUPREME into Cyber Space, effectively locking THE END out of the real world. After Sonic destroyed the other Titans, ignorant to their true purpose, SUPREME was released, and would engage Sonic in a final fight to try to prevent him from unknowingly releasing THE END."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
      "key": "77441195-e3f5-4469-a1c3-c25388423f47",
      "udi": null,
      "values": [
        {
          "alias": "energyMultiplicator",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Boundless"
        },
        {
          "alias": "profilePicture",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": [
            {
              "key": "98f54f81-62b3-4356-989e-e15c7769d888",
              "mediaKey": "1f0e8499-df11-40f9-b007-6da0246fb971",
              "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
              "crops": [],
              "focalPoint": null
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Principles of Ontological Dynamics"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Within the \u0022garden\u0022 that was the field of possibility that prefigured existence were two principles, a gardener and a winnower for the garden. They existed, because they had to exist. They had no antecedent and no constituents. Their clashing would lead to the creation of existence and the universe, where their influence can be found in the form of the Light and the Darkness."
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterTitle",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Bodiless and Inevitable"
        },
        {
          "alias": "groupMembers",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": {
            "contentData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "ba54aa7b-28cc-4e6a-a901-e264b5edaff9",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "2625c45d-60a3-46e3-94db-9732fc9125b7",
                        "mediaKey": "e16c3b19-4648-40a1-b5b4-44892f200f3f",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "b32f7ca7-a9ed-459c-8f07-6cf25d14d79f",
                        "mediaKey": "e16c3b19-4648-40a1-b5b4-44892f200f3f",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Gardener"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Gardener represents the principle of uplifting things that are imperfect in order to make them perfect. It expresses this concept throughout the universe in the form of the Light, a power only able to be given to those the Gardener deems worthy of being uplifted into perfection. The Gardener could best be represented as the one who plants the seeds of life, watching it grow into different complex shapes, some perfect and some not."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "6f386c25-c5f7-4cc6-8761-a63a480078ba",
                "key": "1b567bb1-c669-4237-9afb-8faddf597daf",
                "udi": null,
                "values": [
                  {
                    "alias": "characterName",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Winnower"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "profilePicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "7576ac04-3b30-41a3-94d4-79c6d0856dfd",
                        "mediaKey": "3d49e5c1-1b36-4c5e-b31c-403950e23e9e",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "mainPicture",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": [
                      {
                        "key": "28ef4efe-2043-44d4-817c-8e6f46e0de37",
                        "mediaKey": "3d49e5c1-1b36-4c5e-b31c-403950e23e9e",
                        "mediaTypeAlias": "Image",
                        "crops": [],
                        "focalPoint": null
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "characterSource",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "Destiny"
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "The Winnower represents the principle that perfection in the universe could only be found by attempting to destroy that which is not already perfect, sharpening it until it either fails or becomes the sharpest edge possible. It displays this influence within the universe through the Darkness, a power that needs to be taken by those who want to perfect the universe by force. The Winnower can be represented by the winnowing of the plants grown by the Gardener that fail to withstand its pruning."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ],
            "settingsData": [
              {
                "contentTypeKey": "0255723a-93d7-44f0-846c-23ceb877b4cd",
                "key": "4984ef73-3ab7-47df-822d-f03b77d50caf",
