          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Val Belyx, Gauntlet of Incaru"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Val Belyx oversaw a resurrection ritual\u0027s protection within material space. The ritual was happening in the Ascendant Plane, but a weak seam between the two realities could be found inside a monastery in the Dreaming City, so Val Belyx made sure no intruders could get into the domain. He received tithes from the Ascendant Sentinels blocking the way into his inner chamber. Every three weeks val Belyx is reborn and allowed to continue his task due to Quria\u0027s time loop."
        },
        {
          "alias": "mainPicture",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
