          "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Morgeth was a huge Taken Ogre assigned to defend the entrance to the Keep of Voices. It siphoned massive amounts of power from the Ascendant Plane through Taken Strengths, and would utilize this against a fireteam of Guardians attempting to breach the keep in order to slay Riven."
        },
        {
