          "value": "Varghul, Fragment of Oryx"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Varghul was a servant of Oryx who led Taken forces in the EDZ during the Taken War. As the war concluded, Varghul survived and hid in the Cavern of Souls awaiting a higher power to take command of his will in the place of the now dead Oryx."
        }
      ]
    },
