                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "alias": "details",
                    "culture": null,
                    "editorAlias": null,
                    "segment": null,
                    "value": "An Salaak was horizontally manipulating the fabric of the universe through the use of Taken Blights alongside An Hamaat when the Young Wolf arrived and slew them. Instead of permanently dying as would typially be with Taken in the Ascendant Plane, The two witches keep returning due to the time loop Quria and Riven have put on the Dreaming City."
                  }
                ]
