          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Crorok, Will of Xivu Arath"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2: Forsaken"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Crorok was a Fallen Captain that was Taken by the Witness and placed in servitude to the will of Xivu Arath. She dispatched Crorok to the Dreaming City and tasked him with stealing Awoken relics that were of interest to her. Here Crorok would face the wrath of a Guardian sent by the Awoken to recover their secret artifacts. Crorok is still attempting this same task however as he keeps being brought back to life by Quria\u0027s time loop."
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterVariant",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Material Space"
        },
        {
          "alias": "mainPicture",
