          "segment": null,
          "value": "Dumuzod"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny: The Taken King"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Dumuzod was summoned by a Guardian who had defeated all of his servants individually, and them summoned them again to be fought all together. Due to their deaths Dumuzod arrived in the Founts to strike down the one who was hindering his source of tribute from reaching him. The Guardian would defeat Dumuzod, as it turned out that this was the Young Wolf, who was seeking a Calcified Fragment Dumuzod possessed."
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterVariant",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
