          "alias": "characterName",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Hashlad\u00FBn, Daughter of Crota"
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterSource",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Destiny 2: Shadowkeep"
        },
        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Hashlad\u00FBn was a daughter of Crota, and was incredibly powerful right at birth. She faced down multiple older Hive even as a Thrall, and would have her strength noticed by Crota himself. After the deaths of the Swarm Princes, she took over leadership of the Hidden Swarm. She sought to replace Crota with a worthy champion, and would find a contender in Zulmak."
        },
        {
          "alias": "characterVariant",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Material Space"
        },
