        {
          "alias": "details",
          "culture": null,
          "editorAlias": null,
          "segment": null,
          "value": "Darkblades are powerful Ascendant Knights who follow in the teachings of Alak-Hul, and replicate his style in both visuals and combat. Being upgraded to the level of a Darkblade allowed Kelgorath to become powerful enough to withstand the Moon-destroying power of Rasputin\u0027s Warsat network."
